item.title: Pp6-FEH1
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: Pp6-FEH1 Gene Name: fructan exohydrolase1 Genome: Species: Phleum pratense Functional Descriptions: Pp6-FEH1 encodes an enzyme for degradation of highly polymerized levan and is transcriptionally induced by defoliation in timothy.
